### Test API E-Ticketing Helpdesk

### 1. Register User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get Current User (needs token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Create Ticket (needs token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tikets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "judul": "Tiket Test",
  "deskripsi": "Ini adalah tiket test",
  "kategori": "umum"
}

### 5. List Tickets (needs token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tikets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Get Ticket Detail (needs token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tikets/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Update Ticket Status (needs token)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tikets/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "diproses"
}

### 8. Add Comment (needs token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tikets/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/komentars
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isi_pesan": "Ini komentar test"
}

### 9. Get Dashboard Stats (needs token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Get Notifications (needs token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifikasis
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Mark Notification Read (needs token)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/notifikasis/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
